
# Commands to apply Bayesian neural network to an image classification problem.

net-spec ilog.net 36 80 4 / ih=0.05:4::1.2 bh=0.5:2 ho=2.0:6::4 bo=0.1:1
model-spec ilog.net class

data-spec ilog.net 36 1 4 / idata@1:1000 . idata@1001:3000 .

net-gen ilog.net fix 0.1
mc-spec ilog.net repeat 15 heatbath hybrid 100:10 0.15
net-mc ilog.net 1

mc-spec ilog.net sample-sigmas heatbath hybrid 1500:20 0.3
net-mc ilog.net 2000

net-pred mnpa ilog.net 501:
